\begin_layout Standard
For the choice of wind direction transition density 
\begin_inset Formula $p(b_{t}|b_{t-1})=p(\phi_{t}|b_{t},b_{t-1})=\mathcal{N}(b_{t};b_{t-1},\sigma_{b})$
